    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/6f0b2fa74b84596ae0e7d9c1a7bc9285.avif?t=1772370765\" width=355 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>The world is your weapon in this Earth-slinging <strong>2D platform fighter</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/1ab3cf5a931c1dd4874dca28240b70fb.poster.avif?t=1772370765\" width=680 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/1ab3cf5a931c1dd4874dca28240b70fb.webm?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/1ab3cf5a931c1dd4874dca28240b70fb.mp4?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terra Fighters is a fast-paced brawler blending platform combat, arena destruction, and couch multiplayer mayhem.</strong><br>Pick up the very ground beneath your feet and hurl it at your opponents—the arena itself becomes your weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Hurl the Earth. Hold Your Ground</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/6a52de0ab86e47c7cc49efe8c8db1269.poster.avif?t=1772370765\" width=680 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/6a52de0ab86e47c7cc49efe8c8db1269.webm?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/6a52de0ab86e47c7cc49efe8c8db1269.mp4?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knock your friends off the ground and out of the ring just like king of the hill.</strong> Pick up regular blocks of Earth to throw or special blocks for more impact. Some stages have weather effects that can aid or harm you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Seven Defenders. 6 Unlockable Champions - ALL FREE</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/adb88cc38644bb4fe7ea562911e6baed.poster.avif?t=1772370765\" width=680 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/adb88cc38644bb4fe7ea562911e6baed.webm?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/adb88cc38644bb4fe7ea562911e6baed.mp4?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Start with <strong>seven playable fighters</strong>, and unlock <strong>six hidden champions</strong> as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Story Mode: A Great Cataclysmic Mystery</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/98c482a9b6368519c973c523dc014d10.poster.avif?t=1772370765\" width=680 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/98c482a9b6368519c973c523dc014d10.webm?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209360/extras/98c482a9b6368519c973c523dc014d10.mp4?t=1772370765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cataclysmic time rift fractures the planet. <strong>Kifaru</strong>, the young African prodigy, sets out to uncover its source—only to discover a mystery with links to the past.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Features</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hurl the Earth</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up the ground beneath your feet and use it as a weapon. Throw, charge, catch, and deflect Terra as arenas collapse around you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seven Fighters, 6 more Unlockable - ALL FREE</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle as global defenders—from <strong>Kifaru the Rhino (Africa)</strong> to <strong>Malu the Kangaroo (Australia)</strong>—and unlock <strong>six more fighters</strong>, each with unique elemental Terra abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chaotic Local Battles</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clash in fast-paced <strong>local multiplayer</strong> where curved throws, deflections, and dynamic arenas keep every match unpredictable.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to Learn. Hard to Master.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls meet deep, fast paced combat that rewards timing, positioning, and creative play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode: A Global Mystery</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cataclysmic time rift threatens the planet. Join Kifaru on a journey across the world to uncover the truth behind the chaos.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destructible, Hand-Drawn Arenas</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across dynamic stages inspired by real regions, filled with lightning storms, shifting platforms, and timed collapses.</p></li></ul>",
